<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70B5106060" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "02" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Valve Body Assembly Disassembly and Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B5106037">A/T Assembly Disassembly</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B5106064">A/T Assembly Reassembly</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B5106059">Valve Body Assembly Components</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Do not remove pressure control solenoid valve and/or TCC pressure control solenoid valve, from valve body assembly. Doing so may cause excessive shift shock.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B5106060001">
<title>
Disassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove shift solenoid valve “A” (1) from valve body assembly.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510219.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "48.460mm" ver = "01" gw = "160" gh = "120"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove shift solenoid valve “B” (1) from valve body assembly.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510220.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "49.900mm" ver = "01" gw = "184" gh = "124"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove timing solenoid valve (1) from valve body assembly.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510221.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "47.232mm" ver = "01" gw = "139" gh = "117"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove temperature sensor clamp (1) from valve body assembly.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510222.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "48.206mm" ver = "01" gw = "181" gh = "120"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B5106060002">
<title>
Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
Reverse disassembly procedure noting the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Shift solenoid valves “A” and “B” are identical.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
After applying ATF to new O-rings, fit them to solenoid valves, then install solenoid valves to valve body.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten solenoid valve bolts to specified torque by referring to the following table. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B5106059"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
